wp-content/uploads/hyperbolic/hyperbolic-trig-table.png" alt=3D"hyperbolic-=
table" class=3D"webpexpress-processed"></picture></p>

<p>It's been a long journey, but these functions don't haunt my attic any m=
ore.</p>

